'''Kul''' ama '''[[Kuleyl]]''' ([[Ingiriis]]: heat; [[carabi]]: حرارة) waa [[heerkul]]ka shay, [[curiye]], [[walax]] ama wax kasta leeyahay. Cilmiga [[Fisikis]]ku wuxuu kulka ku sharaxay [[awood]] socota oo u kala gudbeeysa labo walxood oo [[heerkul]]koodu kala sareeyo.

[[Heerkul]]ka waxaa lagu qiyaasaa ''[[Salsiyas]]'' (celsius) ama ''[[Kelfin]]'' (kelvin). 

